    dc:description "FIGURES 4–9. Habitus. 4–6, Beutelius mastersi: 4, dorsal (♂ 9 mm, VIC); 5, same, ventral; 6, dorsal (♀ 8 mm, SAMA); 7, same, ventral; 8–9, B. reidi sp. nov.: 8, dorsal (♂ 5.7 mm, AM); 9, same, ventral." ;
