    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3626582>
    dc:description "FIGURES 85–95. Beutelius spp., mentum: 85–86. 85, B. mastersi, 86, B. rutherfordi (paratype ♂); 87, B. mastersi, mesonotum; 88, B. mastersi, pterothorax, ventral; 89, B. rutherfordi, pterothorax, ventral; aedeagus: 90–95. 90, Omma stanleyi; 91–92, B. mastersi; 93, B. reidi sp. nov.; 94, B. rutherfordi; 95, B. sagitta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3626582/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

